/// This struct defines the shadow mapping using the rule:
465
///   shadow = (mem >> Scale) ADD-or-OR Offset.
466
/// If InGlobal is true, then
467
///   extern char __asan_shadow[];
468
///   shadow = (mem >> Scale) + &__asan_shadow
469
struct ShadowMapping {
470
  int Scale;
471
  uint64_t Offset;
472
  bool OrShadowOffset;
473
  bool InGlobal;
474
};
